  "name": "Klondike Adventure",
  "shortName": "klondike-adventure",
  "description": "<i>Klondike Adventure</i> is the ninth in a series of monthly text adventures for multiple systems.<br><br>You have come to the Klondike in search of Yukon Bill's riches, but you must beware the bitter cold, and other dangers of the Arctic.  Game is a treasure hunt, where the player must locate a gold nugget, gold flakes, a pickax, a fur coat, and the last will and testament of Yukon Bill.  All these five items must be returned to the starting area for a perfect score of 100 points.  During the adventure, the player will beat up a walrus, steal a dead man's boots, meet Santa Claus, steal Rudolph's nose, rob a vending machine, pan for cold, and crawl around inside an oil well.  <br><br>All commands are via 2-word VERB NOUN entries, and game play contains several object puzzles. There is a save and restore feature.",
